and 2013, as well as providing funds for reliable technical support. On the
other hand, we thank the Max Planck President for funding the
${h.external_link('http://clld.org/', 'Cross-Linguistic Linked Data')}
project, into which ValPaL will be eventually integrated.
</p>

<p>
Finally, we thank our student assistants, who have helped us enormously with the
